abstract: Driven column; journalists at Mudfest competition in Washington State pick best sport utility vehicles in six categories.

headline.print_headline: The Best S.U.V.s Emerge From the Mud
headline.main: Video Review: After Some Mud Wrestling, the Best S.U.V.s Emerge

keywords.value: Sports Utility Vehicles and Light Trucks
keywords.name: subject

snippet: Over two days at this year’s Mudfest in the Pacific Northwest, 26 journalists evaluated 27 vehicles, including crossovers, S.U.V.s and pickups.
